    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The remains of buildings or groups of buildings that have been destroyed or are in a state of great disrepair or decay.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
